---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services"
  description="Free leadership courses, personal finance coaching, and 1-on-1 consulting with Jason Ehlinger."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="section-label">What I Offer</span>
    <h1>Real Frameworks.<br/>Real Results.</h1>
    <p>Everything I teach is something I've lived. No theory. No fluff. Start free — go deeper when you're ready.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE COURSES -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Start Here — 100% Free</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:2rem;">Two Complete Free Courses on YouTube</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--gray); max-width:580px; margin:0.75rem auto 0;">No email required. No paywall. Just go watch.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:2rem;">

        <!-- The Forge -->
        <div style="background:var(--black); color:var(--white); border-radius:4px; padding:2.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
          <span class="section-label">13-Part Masterclass</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.8rem; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Forge</h3>
          <p style="color:#bbb; font-style:italic; margin-bottom:1rem; font-size:0.95rem;">Transitioning from Manager to Leader</p>
          <p style="color:#aaa; margin-bottom:1.5rem; flex:1;">A complete course walking you through the transformation from task manager to true leader — covering vision, team building, tough conversations, scaling, accountability, and recovery from failure.</p>
          <ul style="list-style:none; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            {[
              "Develop strong, unique leadership skills",
              "Master tough conversations (5 essential skills)",
              "Create a life-changing vision and turn it into action",
              "Build vulnerability-based trust with your team",
              "Run meetings that actually drive results",
              "How to recover after total failure",
              "Build long-term team commitment",
              "Scale your business as a leader",
            ].map(item => (
              <li style="padding:0.4rem 0; font-size:0.9rem; color:#ccc; border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a;">
                <span style="color:var(--gold); margin-right:0.5rem;">✓</span>{item}
            </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9gAYdG_RPlGi3HtmLBxfCVI0BRa4phIP" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-gold">Watch The Forge Free →</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Lencioni Course -->
        <div style="background:var(--white); border:2px solid #e8e8e8; border-radius:4px; padding:2.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
          <span class="section-label">7-Part Free Course</span>
          <h3 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">The Advantage Framework</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-style:italic; margin-bottom:1rem; font-size:0.95rem;">How to Create a Successful Business</p>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.5rem; flex:1;">Based on Patrick Lencioni's <em>The Advantage</em> — a step-by-step course on building a strong, resilient business from the inside out. Culture, clarity, purpose, and priorities.</p>
          <ul style="list-style:none; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            {[
              "The best way to lead your team (Lencioni's answer)",
              "6-step formula for work satisfaction",
              "Company culture secrets that actually stick",
              "How to clarify your business purpose",
              "Build a winning business strategy",
              "Stop wasting time on wrong priorities",
              "Grow your business with the right advantage",
            ].map(item => (
              <li style="padding:0.4rem 0; font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--gray); border-bottom:1px solid #eee;">
                <span style="color:var(--gold); margin-right:0.5rem;">✓</span>{item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9gAYdG_RPlH3p90RRN9riuhGtMmWO8UC" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-dark">Watch Free on YouTube →</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LEADERSHIP COACHING -->
  <section class="section" id="leadership">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">1-on-1 Leadership Coaching</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">From Manager to Leader</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">The free courses give you the framework. Coaching is where you apply it to your specific situation — your team, your culture, your problems.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2rem;">I've built and led teams at Taika Translations, scaled to 7 figures without losing the mission, and navigated every version of the leadership challenges you're facing. Let's work through yours together.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-dark">Book a Session</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Leadership Audit</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">A deep dive into your team dynamics, systems, and decision-making. You'll walk away with a specific, prioritized action plan.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Vision & Strategy</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Clarify your business purpose, build a mission-driven culture, and create a vision your team will actually follow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Accountability Systems</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Build the structures that let your team own their results — without you micromanaging every detail.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Escape the Operator's Trap</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">If the business can't run without you for a week, that's the first thing we fix.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINANCE -->
  <section class="section section-gray" id="finance">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Personal Finance</span>
          <h2 style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Building Wealth From Zero</h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">777+ free videos on the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);">Vision Tribe Money</a> channel — covering everything from zero-based budgeting to building wealth when you feel stuck.</p>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:2rem;">For those who want to go deeper, I offer private finance coaching — looking at your specific numbers, situation, and goals and building a real plan.</p>
          <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Visiontribemoney" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-gold">Watch Free ↗</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-dark">Private Coaching</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Zero-Based Budgeting</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">A budget method that doesn't feel like a budget. Every dollar has a job before the month starts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Finances in Marriage & Dating</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">Money red flags, green flags, and how to get on the same page as a couple before it becomes a crisis.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.1rem;">Wealth Building From Nothing</h3>
            <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem;">The habits, mindset, and systems behind saving $100k